<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark light" />
    <title>$station.location - $month_name $year_name</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0b1220" media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#f6f9fc" media="(prefers-color-scheme: light)" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="dist/nordlys.css" />
    #if $nordlys_user_css
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="$nordlys_user_css" />
    #end if
  </head>
  <body>
    ## Archive-page shell: the SLE detects the SummaryByMonth timespan and
    ## serializes the [Nordlys][[archive]] layout scoped to this month.
    <script id="nordlys-data" type="application/json">$nordlys_json</script>
    <div id="nordlys-app">
      <div class="nl-fallback">
        <h1>$station.location - $month_name $year_name</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script type="module" src="dist/nordlys.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
